@node "About" "Information"
10,000 is a dice game, written exclusively for DLG.  The object of the game
is to get 10,000 points first.  This is achieved by rolling 6 dice, and
hopefully getting some points from either 1's, 5's, or any group of 3 dice
with the same number.

This game has been tested for almost 1 year on @{"The Fly By Night BBS" alink "FBN" 0}, and I
have squashed all known bugs (hopefully).  So, if you see anything you think
is wrong, let me know!

Although this game is @{"Shareware" alink "Register" 0}, it is FULLY playable for 5 people.  Except
that the benefits of winning the game aren't there, and the winning scores
aren't saved.

In this archive is a program to put in your Login.DLGBatch file that will
show the status of the current game to users when they log in.  In various
games that I've been testing, I've noticed that a LOT more users will play the
game if this program is running.  So, it's up to you, but it makes the game
more fun if you have lots of people playing! :)

@endnode

